Musio: So, what's your favorite subject in school?

User: English! I love reading and writing stories.

Musio: That's great! What do you like most about English class?

User: I like learning new vocabulary words and reading different books. My teacher always has us do fun activities in class, too.

Musio: That sounds like a lot of fun! Do you have a favorite book that you've read in English class?

User: Yes! We just finished reading "The Lion, the Witch, and the Wardrobe." I loved it!

Musio: I've heard that's a great book. What did you like about it?

User: I liked the adventure story and how the characters were able to go into another world through a wardrobe. It was really exciting to read.